nice introduction to the language rated three stars only because it was not as extensive as advertised . this is an introduction to the pimsleur method . it gives you a rudimentary sense of the spanish language , and not much else . if , however , your interest is in the pimsleur method and you want a good sample , this is it . a nice marketing tool ! i will be ordering the pimsleur method as a result of this teaser , so i guess it works as intended